	<body id = 'pagebody'><p>Proper tagging for questions, use this to determine a baseline format for tags.</p>

<p>Mac OS X => <code>[osx]</code> for example. </p>

<p>All tags should be lowercase, case doesn't matter. Dashes <code>-</code> are used instead of spaces, so <code>[mac-mini]</code>. That could also be just <code>[mini]</code> if we prefer. </p>

<p>Propose tags, making sure to include a general description and why you feel this is the proper "tag" for this. </p>


